Follow the steps given below, 


First, 
flex lexeer.l

#this will create a lexel.yy.c file, execute that using

gcc lexer.yy.c -o abc


now, ceate a file example.c and write some code with output in it, and then execute the code using

gcc exampple.c -o def

and now execute both the executables using, 

